title: Crew Show!
description: The million mile LS400 has its first major failure, Matt covets 2 stroke mopeds and an R33 Skyline, a 740 Horsepower Golf is launched, Zack goes offroading in an E30 w/ Musto and Thad and I dread an upcoming Vegas trip.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
